description: Kendall has been waiting to surprise Bruno on his birthday for the longest! She even had to hide his birthday balloon in the oven just so he wouldn’t find it. He was very excited and always snooping around for a sneak peek. The morning of his day of birth, Kendall quietly got out of bed to retrieve his balloon. She set it right on the bed next to him as he slept. Then she woke him up with the softest and most sweetest blowjob. How cute! Bruno liked it, but it wasn’t fully satisfying him. Kendall let Bruno know she would do anything to please him, so he directs her to his drawer of fun. It’s filled with BDSM gear, and Kendall is all about getting dominated and destroyed. Luckily, that’s Bruno’s specialty, especially on his birthday ;). He took the meaning of going ham to another level, leaving Kendall not just sexually off kilter but also smothered in a barrage of jizz. Maybe she can just say it was birthday cake frosting?
title: Birthday Bashing
